author: COMSOL
description: This model shows how to simulate a packed bed latent heat storage tank. Latent heat storage systems store energy - usually energy that is provided by solar collectors - making use of phase change materials. The configuration requires to account for local thermal nonequilibrium between the phase change material paraffin and the charging liquid water.
